CBAY No more texting after this today I have been trying to stay away from ST lately too addictive Both FDA Docs do not care about liver fat They care about liver inflammation and fibrosis 13 of US population has fatty liver but 90 of them do just fine But only a small fraction of them develop NASH Conversely there are many drugs weight reduction surgery diets that cause huge liver fat reduction but have no impact on NASH Sometimes liver fat reduction makes NASH and Fibrosis worse
